VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT SecureStore\.setItemAsync|SecureStore\.getItemAsync
WHEN EXPR MISSING:keychainAccessible|keychainService|requireAuthentication
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Expo SecureStore usage without explicit accessibility and authentication options.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Expo SecureStore Fallback to Unencrypted.
